a $75,000 investment

32:09.728 --> 32:14.332
for a 10% equity stake
in my company, Gently Soap.

32:14.332 --> 32:17.335
Sharks, humans deserve
to feel joy,

32:17.335 --> 32:19.404
and no one
should be robbed of joy

32:19.404 --> 32:22.274
because of
their sensitive skin.

32:22.274 --> 32:25.644
I've had eczema my entire life,
and because of that,

32:25.644 --> 32:29.514
bath products would cause
my skin extreme pain.

32:29.514 --> 32:31.583
Bath bombs, soaps,
and bubble baths

32:31.583 --> 32:34.686
would make my skin feel like...
[ Screams ]

32:34.686 --> 32:38.490
...because they were full
of additives and chemicals.

32:38.490 --> 32:41.226
I thought I was doomed
to a single bar

32:41.226 --> 32:44.629
of boring white soap
for the rest of my life.

32:44.629 --> 32:48.300
So, I set out to create
a joyful, yet gentle,

32:48.300 --> 32:51.303
bathing experience
for people like me,

32:51.303 --> 32:55.474
rooted in the agricultural
legacy of my grandparents.

32:55.474 --> 32:57.442
Aww.
I spent three years

32:57.442 --> 32:59.578
in greenhouses
studying horticulture

32:59.578 --> 33:02.514
to learn more about
the power of plants.

33:02.514 --> 33:06.952
Harnessing that power,
I created Gently Soap,

33:06.952 --> 33:07.719
a line of bath products

33:07.719 --> 33:11.523
that eliminates essential oils
and synthetic fragrances,

33:11.523 --> 33:14.359
the stuff that causes
serious irritations,

33:14.359 --> 33:19.130
but still maintains
an incredible, gentle aroma.

33:19.130 --> 33:20.498
People with
ultra-sensitive skin

33:20.498 --> 33:23.535
finally have a choice
and can indulge in

33:23.535 --> 33:27.506
light and clean botanical soaps
that are ultra gentle,

33:27.506 --> 33:31.176
more sustainable,
and filled with joy.
[ Chuckles ]

33:31.176 --> 33:33.245
It's not just for people
with sensitive skin.

33:33.245 --> 33:34.579
It's for everybody.

33:34.579 --> 33:38.116
So, Sharks, who would like
to help me

33:38.116 --> 33:40.285
in completely washing away

33:40.285 --> 33:43.622
the bathing industry
expectations as we know it?

33:43.622 --> 33:47.225
Sharks, each of you have
all four Gently Soap bars

33:47.225 --> 33:48.393
right in front of you.

33:48.393 --> 33:51.363
