34:15.654 --> 34:17.355
Dunning: The smell that
you're smelling is actually

34:17.355 --> 34:19.157
from proprietary
herbal infusions

34:19.157 --> 34:20.625
that I created
from my greenhouse work.

34:20.625 --> 34:22.394
Proprietary?
