Yeah.

35:57.489 --> 36:00.392
And this is an increase of 55%
in just two decades.

36:00.392 --> 36:01.726
It's increasing.
Yeah.
Yes.

36:01.726 --> 36:03.261
Growing market.
So people with
hypersensitive skin

36:03.261 --> 36:04.462
is growing exponentially,

36:04.462 --> 36:06.331
but there's still
only one bar of soap

36:06.331 --> 36:07.465
to take care
of that entire population.

36:07.465 --> 36:10.135
How did you come up
with $11 a bar?

36:10.135 --> 36:12.203
Look, I'm not -- I'm just --
I'm stunned,

36:12.203 --> 36:13.271
because this is expensive.
Yeah.

36:13.271 --> 36:14.439
But this is
so beautiful.

36:14.439 --> 36:16.107
This is such
an elevated product.
I get it, but...

36:16.107 --> 36:17.409
It's a work
of art!

36:17.409 --> 36:18.643
It's gorgeous.
I just want to know
what the other pricings are

36:18.643 --> 36:23.281
for other soaps that also
solve for sensitive skin.

36:23.281 --> 36:25.250
Right. They're around
$14 to $16.

36:25.250 --> 36:28.253
I mean, I designed it
out of necessity for me.

36:28.253 --> 36:30.522
So, I've literally had eczema
my entire life.

36:30.522 --> 36:32.457
When I was 3 years old,
my hair fell out

36:32.457 --> 36:33.658
due to scalp eczema.
Wow.

36:33.658 --> 36:37.429
And kids are kind of cruel,
and -- sorry --

36:37.429 --> 36:39.330
[Voice breaking] I experienced
a lot of bullying because of it,

36:39.330 --> 36:42.300
because my skin
was just really bad.

36:42.300 --> 36:43.468
And, of course,
like, middle school,

36:43.468 --> 36:45.437
you want boys to look at you
at that age,

36:45.437 --> 36:47.338
and that obviously
wasn't happening.

36:47.338 --> 36:50.608
So it took a really, like,
hard hit on my confidence.

36:50.608 --> 36:52.477
I would walk down
aisles and aisles

36:52.477 --> 36:56.114
of all my favorite stores,
pharmacies, retail,

36:56.114 --> 36:57.449
and I couldn't find it for me.

36:57.449 --> 37:00.251
So, Gently Soap was born
out of necessity.

37:00.251 --> 37:01.419
It was born out of my passion.

37:01.419 --> 37:03.321
It was born out of
my agricultural legacy.

37:03.321 --> 37:04.456
Wow.
Good for you.
Good for you.

37:04.456 --> 37:06.257
I'm so proud of you
for turning that adversity

37:06.257 --> 37:08.526
into something so beautiful.

37:08.526 --> 37:11.129
I love that
you solved a problem

37:11.129 --> 37:13.231
that came
from your own need.

37:13.231 --> 37:15.266
I think you've done
a beautiful job

37:15.266 --> 37:17.502
of putting this together.

37:17.502 --> 37:20.371
It's just not the right business
for me at this time,

37:20.371 --> 37:23.007
because of something else
that I am working on.

37:23.007 --> 37:24.175
Okay.
Good luck.

37:24.175 --> 37:26.044
But I'm out.

37:26.044 --> 37:27.178
Yeah, you know what?

37:27.178 --> 37:29.047
It's just not something
