37:29.047 --> 37:31.116
I'm not a luxurious soap
person.

37:31.116 --> 37:32.217
Maybe someday.
I understand that.

37:32.217 --> 37:33.518
So for those reasons,
I'm out.

37:33.518 --> 37:35.420
But congrats.
Yeah. Congrats.
Thank you, Mark.
Thank you.

37:35.420 --> 37:38.123
I have been very fortunate
enough that I don't --

37:38.123 --> 37:39.190
I don't really do much
for my skin.

37:39.190 --> 37:40.225
And one of the only things

37:40.225 --> 37:41.359
people compliment me on
is my skin,

37:41.359 --> 37:42.560
and I gotta
thank my mommy.
It looks amazing.

37:42.560 --> 37:44.195
She gave it to me
for my birthday.

37:44.195 --> 37:45.463
And that's all I know,
right?

37:45.463 --> 37:47.265
So, I don't believe
I can help you

37:47.265 --> 37:50.235
as much as one other person
on this panel.

37:50.235 --> 37:51.269
[ Laughs ]

37:51.269 --> 37:53.204
So, I'm out.
Okay. Thank you, Daymond.

37:53.204 --> 37:54.539
The thing that got me
on this deal --

37:54.539 --> 37:57.242
I love your story,
got all that.
Thank you. Thank you so much.

37:57.242 --> 37:59.277
What I find so attractive
about you --

37:59.277 --> 38:00.311
You're wonderful,

38:00.311 --> 38:01.780
but your margins
are even more beautiful.

38:01.780 --> 38:05.283
Thank you.
So, tell me about
customer-acquisition costs.

38:05.283 --> 38:09.287
We're able to get customers
for about $5.83,

38:09.287 --> 38:12.223
but our average order value
is $42.38.

38:12.223 --> 38:13.658
$5.83 is
customer acquisition?
Wow.

38:13.658 --> 38:15.226
Yes.
I love the fact
that you know that.

38:15.226 --> 38:16.961
So, we're trying to stay
between $5 and $15

38:16.961 --> 38:18.229
as we continue to grow.

38:18.229 --> 38:20.832
I smell a royalty.
Oh, boy.

38:20.832 --> 38:25.136
[ Laughs ] Okay.
Yeah, because you can afford
to pay me a royalty.

