And I'm all over it
trying to acquire customers.

39:11.182 --> 39:13.151
That's all I'll do
all day.

39:13.151 --> 39:15.320
Kristen, I am
mesmerized by you.

39:15.320 --> 39:18.223
You literally glow
from the inside out.

39:18.223 --> 39:20.358
And there's two types
of entrepreneurs.

39:20.358 --> 39:22.493
There's, you know,
the Mr. Wonderfuls of the world.

39:22.493 --> 39:25.430
They're analyzing the market,
looking for the white space,

39:25.430 --> 39:27.532
and being very analytical
about it.
Yeah.

39:27.532 --> 39:30.101
And then there are
passion-driven entrepreneurs,

39:30.101 --> 39:31.302
and I've always been
